name: 雛菜
text: あは～、準決勝\n始まるって～～～

name: プロデューサー
text: ああ、雛菜はいつも通りだな
trans: Yeah. And I see that Hinana is the same as always.

name: 雛菜
text: へ～？\nうん、雛菜はいつも雛菜だよ～？
trans:
Heh～?
Yup, Hinana is always Hinana, you know～?

name: 雛菜
text: え～、なんで笑うの～\n雛菜、おもしろいこと言った～？
trans:
Eh, why are you laughing～?
Did Hinana say something funny～?

name: プロデューサー
text: い、いや、すまん\n雛菜が頼もしくて、つい
trans:
No, I'm sorry.
It's just that Hinana is always so reliable, I couldn't help it.

name: 雛菜
text: どうせ笑うなら、\n雛菜のステージ見て笑ってよ～
trans: Laugh all you want, but do it while watching Hinana's performance～

name: 雛菜
text: すっごく楽しくて、しあわせ～って、ね？
trans: Because it will be full of happiness and fun, right～?
